OL,3,CProbation chief warns 'things will go
OL,4,Cwrong' with early prison release scheme
OL,6,FThose released early will serve the
OL,7,Frest of their sentence under "strict"
OL,8,Flicensing conditions in the community,
OL,9,Fthe government has said, with the
OL,10,Fprison and probation service given
OL,11,Feight weeks to plan for the scheme.
OL,13,FMartin Jones, who became chief
OL,14,Finspector in March, told The Times
OL,15,Fthat there are "no risk free options
OL,16,Favailable" although extra strain will
OL,17,Fbe put on the probation service.
