OL,3,CProbation chief warns 'things will go
OL,4,Cwrong' with early prison release scheme
OL,6,F"What I think you should, you should
OL,7,Fstart to see, at least, is that if
OL,8,Fpeople have to focus on those, that
OL,9,Fthey start to identify where things go
OL,10,Fwrong, and they draw lessons from that
OL,11,Fquite quickly."
OL,13,FMr Jones added: "I also think there's
OL,14,Fa little bit of a numbers game to some
OL,15,Fextent, you're rolling the dice all
OL,16,Fthe time in relation to serious
OL,17,Ffurther offences.
