OL,3,CProbation chief warns 'things will go
OL,4,Cwrong' with early prison release scheme
OL,6,F"You know, ultimately, if you release
OL,7,Fthousands of people, a number of those
OL,8,Fcases will ultimately, sadly, there
OL,9,Fwill be things that will go wrong."
OL,11,FAt least 1,000 new trainee probation
OL,12,Fofficers will be recruited by the end
OL,13,Fof March 2025, according to the
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,16,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer,
OL,17,Fspeaking to broadcasters in Berlin on
OL,18,FWednesday, also said more prisons will
OL,19,Fbe built to manage overcrowding once
OL,20,Fthe government gets its "hands on the
OL,21,Fplanning laws".
