OL,3,CProbation chief warns 'things will go
OL,4,Cwrong' with early prison release scheme
OL,6,FHe said the lack of prisons being
OL,7,Fbuilt is one of the reasons for the
OL,8,Fcurrent capacity crisis in jails
OL,9,Facross the UK.
OL,11,FSir Keir previously described the
OL,12,Fdecision to release prisoners early as
OL,13,Fa difficult one, and "goes against the
OL,14,Fgrain of everything I've ever done".
OL,16,FParliament last month approved
OL,17,Fregulations to reduce the amount of
OL,18,Ftime prisoners must spend in jail
OL,19,Fbefore they are automatically
OL,20,Freleased, from 50% of their sentence
OL,21,Fto 40%.
