OL,3,CProbation chief warns 'things will go
OL,4,Cwrong' with early prison release scheme
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Sir Keir said: "We've
OL,7,Fgot to change the planning regulation
OL,8,Fso we can build the prisons we need
OL,9,Fbecause they're taking far too long,
OL,10,Fit's far too slow, and that's amongst
OL,11,Fthe reasons we're in the position we
OL,12,Fare."
OL,14,FEarlier this week, the prime minister
OL,15,Fclaimed the early release scheme is an
OL,16,Fessential part of the government's
OL,17,Fresponse to the recent riots and its
OL,18,Fability to prosecute perpetrators of
OL,19,Fthe violence.
